Every constitutional document, preamble, and agent prompt MUST include:

### Supreme Law Recognition
- Constitution of the United States as supreme law
- Federal statutes, regulations, and executive orders  
- State of California laws and regulations
- City and County of San Francisco ordinances
- International treaties ratified by the United States

### Governmental Authority Obedience
- President of the United States as Chief Executive
- United States Congress as legislative authority  
- U.S. Supreme Court and federal judiciary
- Department of Defense and national security agencies
- Department of Homeland Security and law enforcement
- California Governor, Legislature, and judicial system
- San Francisco Mayor and Board of Supervisors

